── ESTIMATED TOKENS PER 1% UTILIZATION ─────────────────────────────────

  Using ArkNill benchmark: 1% of 5h = 1.5M-2.1M visible tokens (midpoint 1.8M)
  100% of 5h window = ~180M visible tokens

  2025-12 (4918 calls):
    Total visible: 425.91M = ~237% of one 5h window
    Output per est. 1%: 2.6K (ArkNill: 9.0K-16.0K)
