── KEY FINDINGS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  1. QUOTA MULTIPLIER from cache_read weight change:
     Feb: 219.13M (0x) → 2153.59M (1x) = 9.8x increase
     Mar: 394.24M (0x) → 4838.03M (1x) = 12.3x increase

  2. CACHE READ SHARE of visible tokens:
     Feb: 90.2% of visible tokens
     Mar: 92.9% of visible tokens

  3. OUTPUT (5x) SHARE of quota:
     Under 0x: Feb 5.1%, Mar 18.0%
     Under 1x: Feb 0.5%, Mar 1.5%
     When cache_read counts, output's share shrinks but its absolute cost stays the same.
